Package application.models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Booking
    Purpose: Booking class containing fields and methods pertaining to a single booking Description: Contains information about the booking in the form of String fields, and a list of seats for the Booking (note: unlike the one in Screening, the seats list in Booking does not contain information about any unbooked seats; there are no false values in the HashMap
    Customer
    Purpose: Customer model Description: Extends User, includes customer details and setter/getter methods
    Employee
    Purpose: Employee model Description: Extends user; used to identify when a cinema employee (as opposed to a customer) is logged in
    Film
    Purpose: Film class containing fields and methods pertaining to a single film Description: Contains information about the film in the form of String fields, the image for the film, and a list of Screenings; along with getter methods and methods for managing the list of Screenings
    Screening
    Purpose: Screening class containing fields and methods pertaining to a single screening Description: Contains information about the screening in the form of String fields, a list of seats in the screening (with information on whether or not each seat is booked); along with getter methods and methods for managing the list of seats.
    SuperModel
    Purpose: Ancestor/parent class for all models; meant to contain fields and methods potentially useful to all models.
    User
    Purpose: Abstract User model (extended by Customer and Employee) Description: Contains details and setter/getter methods common to both Customers and Employees
